strings:
<voice_0x01001D03><se_high>Princess Medea: ...Do I look grey to you?
...No? Thank goodness.
I was worried that being here
might affect us somehow.
<voice_0x01001D04><se_high>Princess Medea: At first, I thought the World of Darkness was no more than a black void, but I see now that I was wrong. It simply lacks colour.
<voice_0x01001D05><se_high>Princess Medea: It seems a rather melancholy place to me...but I wonder if the people who live here would find our world bright and garish.
<voice_0x01001D06><se_high>Princess Medea: I must admit, there is something slightly romantic about this shadowy landscape...though I certainly wouldn't want to stay forever.
<voice_0x01001D07><se_high>Princess Medea: I mean...it can be a little scary in the dark.

<voice_0x01001D08><se_high>Princess Medea: But as long as I have you by my side,
I know I have nothing to be frightened of.
